This is "mothcdc" (formerly "mincatcdc"), an altered version of the original MinCDC software by Orson
Peters (https://github.com/orlp/mincdc). It is not the original software: the
fork adds a caterpillar coalescing layer, a SIMD prefetch soundness fix, and
additional tests. These modifications are released under the same Zlib license
below.

